Assertion means validation


Types of assertion

1. Hard Assertion
2.Soft Assertion

Hard Assertion ----
=====================

We can access it from Assert class

Assert.assertEquals(true,true);
Assert.assertTrue(true);
Assert.assertNotEquals(true,false);


Method are static

* If hard assertion failed test of rest of the statement will not be executed


Soft Assertion

-> We can access it through SoftAssert object

-> SoftAssert sf = new SoftAssert();

sf.assertTrue();

sf.assertAll();

--> If soft assert will fail rest of the statements will be exeute

